{"tid":324003,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"做過旅遊書，你問我答","createTime":"2017-07-16T05:59:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T14:20:39.000Z","uid":128961,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3b74b2f8041e40051fec38c60f829ba6e7b3c21d","tid":324003,"uid":128961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:59:53.000Z","msg":"見到近排旅遊書咁多話題，開個post講下<br />\n<br />\n邊間出版社就唔講啦，係香港數一數二最多人買嘅旅遊書<br />\n<br />\n每次出書時間表好趕，只有兩三個月就要做好一本書，好多時寫緊書就要開始搵下本書嘅景點，所以如果part到個hea同事，成本書就質素注定差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身我對旅遊好有興趣，一開始真心想做好每本書，但原來做得多又比美術部diu，同事又唔想同你一齊顛，所以之後都愈做愈無火......但求無錯就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最可怕係公司內有長年係度嘅老屎忽，同埋返工似返學黃馬褂，就算做得點好都係無人理，所以我已經早走早著啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b2a0236b79f66ff0157511edd3bb76bc0e5a49","tid":324003,"uid":103006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:12:51.000Z","msg":"好唔好搵先"},{"pid":"e0f2249dbbbb732429559c25bc919102913405e9","tid":324003,"uid":128961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:18:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好唔好搵先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪又係萬幾蚊，但最慘係做耐咗人工都唔高得去邊"},{"pid":"642613cd7b0b7875b355b388cb8dd70301fa4893","tid":324003,"uid":99610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:49:38.000Z","msg":"做過旅行社走去做有冇so?"},{"pid":"8a025c0c2becce0dddd71c8e2dfe64c6c73414c7","tid":324003,"uid":64067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:51:19.000Z","msg":"d地點點揀出黎？"},{"pid":"13624215744740b94cf882d5edd62b934c6aab9a","tid":324003,"uid":128961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:59:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做過旅行社走去做有冇so?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該都有幫助，最重要係寫野OK，對旅遊有熱誠！"},{"pid":"0d1fd453d7209a28ae14a65bb9e41500317279dd","tid":324003,"uid":128961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:03:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>d地點點揀出黎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都離唔開睇blog(當地人介紹)、新聞(最新開幕)，有時如果同旅遊局合作，就會由佢地個邊介紹下<br />\n<br />\n不過做到後期個市唔好，上司可能會叫記者問人拎發相，就咁寫稿，咁樣寫出黎一定係伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5261e53f4148f4f0889a3203bd1a82ebd66d6eaa","tid":324003,"uid":77541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T13:47:01.000Z","msg":"建唔建議大家跟旅遊書去旅行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb1cb3cfcfe81366d6ed8533e940427179dc308c","tid":324003,"uid":18926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T13:53:08.000Z","msg":"點入行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c9ef5f12601ebec7d9111fc64c03a76175a540","tid":324003,"uid":46020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T14:20:39.000Z","msg":"Fresh grad 無相關經驗點入行？<br />\n人工點？<br />\n我好有興趣"}]}